**Creating a game that fits inside a QR code.**

Welcome to my YSWS project. This game is fully encoded into a QR code for anyone to scan and play!

## Play the Game!
You can play the game right here in your browser. Simply click the link below and use the **arrow keys** to move!

[Launch the Game](pdl.sharkingstudios.hackclub.app/test)

or copy the code straight into your browser!
```
data:text/html;base64,
```

## Scan the QR Code
You can also scan the QR code below to play here:
